title: Grateful Dead Live at Niagara Falls Convention Center on 1984-04-17
lineage: Dat (Sony R500) > Tascam DA-3000 >Adobe Audition CC 2015 > Samplitude Pro X3 Suite > FLAC/
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, Dire Wolf, Minglewood Blues, Row Jimmy, My Brother Esau, Ramble On Rose, Looks Like Rain-> Deal

Set 2

Beer Barrel Polka, Help On The Way-> Slipknot!-> Franklin's Tower-> Women Are Smarter-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Black Peter-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: Touch Of Gray

Slipknot Black Peter  Just another KILLER 84' show. H/SF & Black Peter are the highlights. One of my favorite Black Peters!
